http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Art-of-Living-%E2%80%98I-Excel-I-Lead%E2%80%99-workshop-from-today/article14026448.ece

The local chapter of Art of Living is organising a three-day leadership workshop ‘I Excel I Lead’ for entrepreneurs and senior management staff on Friday, Saturday and Sunday.The 18-hour-long session is meant to help entrepreneurs and professionals improve their decision-making and leadership skills. Yadava Muthappa, an IT professional, who worked in diverse fields, will be the resource person who would give insights into understanding the mind-body complex, leadership and its application, discovering health and power of one-power of many, among a host of other topics.The three-day programme will be conducted at Hotel Palm Beach. On Friday, the session will be held from 9:30 a.m. to 6:30 p.m., on Saturday and Sunday the workshop will be held between 4 p.m. and 9 p.m. Further details can be had by contacting 9441824864 or send an email to:ranikrishna.s@gmail.com.